On every team there is one player who is the king. This player receives resistance 1 and 15 hearts. When the king dies, everyone on the
team gets weakness for the rest of the game.

This skript uses the variables from D4's team manager. Edits of D4's skript will probably work too.

Commands:
Operators only:
/kings set <player>     - Sets a certain player as the king of their team
/kings remove <player>  - Removes a certain player as the king of their team
/kings reset            - Resets the kings
/kings apply            - Applies effects to the kings
Everyone:
/kings list             - Lists the kings
